<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Personnel">Personnel</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Into_the_Gap&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Personnel">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<dl>
<dt>Thompson Twins</dt>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Tom_Bailey_(musician)" title="Tom Bailey (musician)">Tom Bailey</a>&#160;– vocals; guitars, <a href="/wiki/Contrabass" title="Contrabass">contrabass</a>; piano, synthesizer; harmonica; drum programming</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Joe_Leeway" title="Joe Leeway">Joe Leeway</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Sequential_Circuits_Prophet-5" title="Sequential Circuits Prophet-5">Prophet-5</a> synthesizer; percussion; backing vocals</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Alannah_Currie" title="Alannah Currie">Alannah Currie</a>&#160;– drums; percussion, marimba, xylophone; backing vocals</li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dt>Production team</dt>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Alex_Sadkin" title="Alex Sadkin">Alex Sadkin</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Audio_engineering" title="Audio engineering" class="mw-redirect">engineer</a>, <a href="/wiki/Record_producer" title="Record producer">producer</a></li>
<li>Tom Bailey&#160;– producer</li>
<li>Chris Dickey&#160;– assistant engineer</li>
<li>Frank Gibson&#160;– assistant engineer</li>
<li>Steve Dewey&#160;– assistant engineer</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Phil_Thornalley" title="Phil Thornalley">Phil Thornalley</a>&#160;– recorder; mixer</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Ted_Jensen" title="Ted Jensen">Ted Jensen</a>&#160;– mastering</li>
</ul>
